1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,790
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:49,980
[Episode 13]

19
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:51,760
I'll go with you.

20
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:52,560
-No.
-No.
-No.

21
00:02:53,050 --> 00:02:53,610
Master.

22
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:54,660
You haven't recovered yet,

23
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:55,680
so you mustn't risk it.

24
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,170
I'm fine now.

25
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:59,400
You guys are making me look like a loser.

26
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:04,850
Fan Yue is never a loser,

27
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:07,180
nor would he ever see himself as one.

28
00:03:07,210 --> 00:03:09,520
Don't you ever say something like that again.

29
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,990
Then let me go with you.

30
00:03:13,650 --> 00:03:14,530
I know that

31
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:16,380
entering the palace this time is fraught with danger.

32
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,810
But how could you expect me to watch you

33
00:03:17,810 --> 00:03:18,870
risk your life?

34
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,770
Have you considered my feelings?

35
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:25,050
If you stay silent,

36
00:03:25,890 --> 00:03:27,090
that means you agree.

37
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:35,660
Tian Huo is not here.

38
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,960
No, don't!

39
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,750
I'm not looking for Tian Huo.

40
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:42,610
I'm here for Ms. Bai.

41
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:43,150
You...

42
00:03:43,180 --> 00:03:44,040
Looking for me?

43
00:03:44,650 --> 00:03:45,490
Ms. Bai,

44
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:47,100
thank you for saving my life last night.

45
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,900
I, Mu Jiu, always return favors.

46
00:03:52,180 --> 00:03:53,560
This second Heart Flame...

47
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,500
I'll give it to you.

48
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:56,700
Consider it as repaying your kindness.

49
00:03:57,890 --> 00:03:59,490
I’ll take you up on that then.

50
00:04:04,170 --> 00:04:05,600
Huo, do you think...

51
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,600
I'm a generous person?

52
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:11,540
By the way,

53
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:13,190
you guys were talking about...

54
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,380
the Underground Palace.

55
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:15,380
This is it, right?

56
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,839
You eavesdropped on us again?

57
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:20,700
No.

58
00:04:20,730 --> 00:04:21,660
I didn't mean it.

59
00:04:21,670 --> 00:04:22,660
I happen to have heard it

60
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,120
when I came to deliver the Heart Flame.

61
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,760
I swear

62
00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:25,840
I will never tell anyone.

63
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,420
Itching for trouble again, aren't you?

64
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:28,520
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

65
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:29,880
I'm here to help you.

66
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:30,640
Really!

67
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:31,700
How'll you help?

68
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:32,610
Wait.

69
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,490
Are you serious about helping?

70
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,170
Of course.

71
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:40,110
When we were in Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

72
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:40,960
we were...

73
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:43,490
inseparable as we faced life and death together.

74
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:44,040
Right, Huo?

75
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,420
Quit pretending to be friendly.

76
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:47,040
Tian Huo didn't even enter the realm of resentment.

77
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,310
We don't need your help.

78
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:50,310
-We need his help.
-We need his help.

79
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:57,020
That pesky fox is so annoying.

80
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,960
And yet, Bai Shuo

81
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:59,290
believed his nonsense.

82
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:00,840
Don't worry about Mu Jiu.

83
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,160
Just remember,

84
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:03,600
no matter what happens tonight,

85
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,480
you must protect Master.

86
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,230
Understood.

87
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,600
Actually, our master hasn't been

88
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,060
happy all these years.

89
00:05:10,090 --> 00:05:10,990
It'd be nice

90
00:05:11,010 --> 00:05:12,230
if he can maintain

91
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:13,770
this disposition.

92
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:15,830
There are no "what ifs" in this world.

93
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,800
If our master hadn't forsaken

94
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,480
his former innocence,

95
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,360
he wouldn't have lived to this day.

96
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,240
M-Master.

97
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:29,680
I...

98
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:30,690
I was talking nonsense just now.

99
00:05:30,690 --> 00:05:31,480
Regardless of how you may be,

100
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,060
I will still like you

101
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,360
and be loyal to you.

102
00:05:33,409 --> 00:05:35,050
What was Fan Yue like before?

103
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:38,010
How did Fan Yue

104
00:05:38,090 --> 00:05:39,670
fall in love with Bai Shuo?

105
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,490
Fall in...

106
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:42,620
love?

107
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:50,520
This is the entire process of how

108
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,920
you got to know Bai Shuo.

109
00:05:52,530 --> 00:05:54,920
From Unbridled Pavilion to Bright Moon Palace,

110
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,030
to Lanling,

111
00:05:56,050 --> 00:05:57,810
and now in Outlanders' City,

112
00:05:58,050 --> 00:06:00,320
I can't tell at which part did you fall in love.

113
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:00,920
Master.

114
00:06:00,940 --> 00:06:02,200
Don't be fooled by her.

115
00:06:03,210 --> 00:06:05,460
Are you sure you didn't miss out on any details?

116
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:06,700
Absolutely not.

117
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:07,600
Master.

118
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:08,930
Regardless,

119
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,250
we had something to do with

120
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,130
Bai Shuo's father's death.

121
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:14,620
Although we may be allies with Bai Shuo now,

122
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,830
it's only so that we can activate the Contemplation Stone.

123
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,030
Sooner or later,

124
00:06:18,050 --> 00:06:20,710
we and Bai Shuo are bound to go our separate ways.

125
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:40,810
Xi.

126
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:42,960
Fenlan Banquet is happening tonight.

127
00:06:43,060 --> 00:06:45,780
Love, hate, kill, greed.

128
00:06:45,810 --> 00:06:47,850
I don't know which Contemplation is next,

129
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:52,909
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

130
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:50,210
or what might actually happen.

131
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:52,290
No matter what threats lie ahead,

132
00:06:52,290 --> 00:06:53,420
I'm not afraid.

133
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:55,600
But Fan Yue...

134
00:06:55,970 --> 00:07:01,830
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

135
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,930
I only remember you.

136
00:07:00,770 --> 00:07:02,230
You're the one who saved me

137
00:07:03,050 --> 00:07:04,110
and treats me well.

138
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:11,980
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

139
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,680
Be careful!

140
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,080
Blocking the knife for me?

141
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:11,760
You could have died, you know?

142
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:12,740
I'm fine.

143
00:07:12,610 --> 00:07:17,800
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

144
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:14,240
I said I would protect you.

145
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,680
I won't forget

146
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:16,980
these words.

147
00:07:18,350 --> 00:07:19,460
Luckily,

148
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,600
I still have you.

149
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:25,660
♫Across thousands of miles♫

150
00:07:23,500 --> 00:07:24,960
He's the Demon King of the Polar Region.

151
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,840
He couldn't let his guard down.

152
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:27,960
We demons

153
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,380
fought among a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood.

154
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:32,140
You will never understand

155
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:35,090
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

156
00:07:32,170 --> 00:07:34,030
what our master has been through.

157
00:07:37,810 --> 00:07:44,890
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

158
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:50,680
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

159
00:07:56,170 --> 00:07:57,630
Must you enter the palace?

160
00:07:58,790 --> 00:07:59,870
I have to go.

161
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:03,410
Is it because of the Contemplation Stone?

162
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:05,120
Some things speak for themselves,

163
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,850
even if you don't mention them.

164
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:08,740
You chose to travel with the demons because

165
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:12,000
you wanted to gather the Five Contemplations and become stronger, right?

166
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,930
Is the next Contemplation here in Outlanders' City?

167
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:17,460
Yes.

168
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:19,990
Ultimately, this is my own problem.

169
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:21,570
Chong Zhao.

170
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:24,990
I know you don’t care about that Wutong Spirit Pill.

171
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:25,970
Just stay here in the inn.

172
00:08:25,970 --> 00:08:27,300
Don't go and risk yourself.

173
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:28,730
You may have things you want to do,

174
00:08:28,730 --> 00:08:30,720
and the Eternals are not willing to support you.

175
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,470
Shuo.

176
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:33,610
But, I will.

177
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,740
So,

178
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,860
what’s your plan for tonight?

179
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,920
Who was it who said the Outlander Palace was dangerous,

180
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,380
but is still going anyway?

181
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:55,490
Let's go.

182
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,380
Bei Chen.

183
00:08:56,970 --> 00:08:58,880
You know the Outlander Palace would be dangerous,

184
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,060
yet you're still going?

185
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:01,050
Ms. Bai.

186
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:02,570
I know you mean well.

187
00:09:03,930 --> 00:09:06,330
But Kunlun collapsed a thousand years ago.

188
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:07,530
Although it has been rebuilt,

189
00:09:07,530 --> 00:09:09,590
we have yet to regain our vitality.

190
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,820
Kunlun needs the Wutong Spirit Pill.

191
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:13,280
I'm here by order of my master.

192
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,500
Although I know there's not much hope,

193
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:15,640
I can't just give up.

194
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,270
I'll do my best.

195
00:09:26,930 --> 00:09:28,850
You won't be able to talk them out of it.

196
00:09:28,850 --> 00:09:31,020
The disciples of Kunlun never let their master down.

197
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:32,260
Aren't you the same?

198
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,980
The responsibility of Lanling

199
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:36,110
has always rested with you, hasn't it?

200
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,280
Let's go.

201
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,950
We should set off.

202
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:54,890
I'll be alright entering the palace myself.

203
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:56,820
You all should stay here in the inn.

204
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:58,750
You think there's danger?

205
00:09:58,770 --> 00:10:00,940
If we don't come back in four hours,

206
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:02,140
don't hesitate.

207
00:10:02,170 --> 00:10:05,450
Leave Outlanders' City immediately and report it to our master.

208
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:06,650
Yes.

209
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,120
[Peace and joy]

210
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,740
Today is the Fenlan Festival.

211
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,460
There are no longer deities in this world.

212
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:57,200
Who are they making their wishes to?

213
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,260
To themselves.

214
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:02,010
The Outlanders were abandoned by the various races

215
00:11:02,010 --> 00:11:03,660
and had no deity to pray to.

216
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,590
By writing their wishes on the lantern,

217
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:05,210
[Fortune]

218
00:11:05,620 --> 00:11:07,480
they are reminding themselves to

219
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:10,880
rely on no one but themselves for whatever they desire.

220
00:11:11,010 --> 00:11:11,930
That's right.

221
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,400
Indeed, in this world,

222
00:11:13,540 --> 00:11:16,450
it's better to rely on yourself than to depend on others.

223
00:11:16,450 --> 00:11:17,360
Shuo.

224
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,580
Let's go set off a sky lantern too.

225
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,340
Okay.

226
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,620
It's not yet time for the banquet anyway.

227
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,240
[Contemplation]

228
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,860
[Contemplation] [Peace]

229
00:11:34,140 --> 00:11:35,240
Take it.

230
00:11:38,370 --> 00:11:39,040
This is yours.

231
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:39,720
Thank you.

232
00:11:47,300 --> 00:11:48,520
What did you write?

233
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,510
Nothing.

234
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:53,400
Someone as cold-hearted as you has secrets too?

235
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:17,140
If it weren't for this moment

236
00:12:17,230 --> 00:12:19,160
and the tough battle ahead,

237
00:12:19,330 --> 00:12:21,420
this would be the most memorable scene

238
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:23,500
I've ever witnessed.

239
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,560
Shuo.

240
00:12:32,660 --> 00:12:33,780
We're not lovers.

241
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:38,680
Right?

242
00:12:40,850 --> 00:12:42,330
I've asked Cang Shan

243
00:12:43,170 --> 00:12:44,770
how we got to know each other.

244
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:48,840
-Actually...
-I’m sorry.

245
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:53,860
About everything that has happened before.

246
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:54,980
And also,

247
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:57,080
regarding your father...

248
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:01,150
I'm sorry.

249
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:06,060
How I wish I am not him,

250
00:13:07,490 --> 00:13:09,220
but how I also wish I am him.

251
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:12,210
At least he can protect you.

252
00:13:17,490 --> 00:13:18,690
How beautiful!

253
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:20,080
Fireworks!

254
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,180
So beautiful.

255
00:13:32,890 --> 00:13:34,200
It's time to enter the palace.

256
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,130
Shuo.

257
00:13:38,710 --> 00:13:40,830
I don't know when he'll be back.

258
00:13:41,650 --> 00:13:42,610
But for now,

259
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:45,020
let's say our goodbyes.

260
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:57,730
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

261
00:14:00,620 --> 00:14:04,230
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

262
00:14:05,170 --> 00:14:09,400
♫You are my determined way home♫

263
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:15,750
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

264
00:14:15,830 --> 00:14:19,860
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

265
00:14:20,290 --> 00:14:22,750
♫Let's never let go♫

266
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:25,820
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

267
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,510
Are you angry?

268
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:51,760
Just now, I...

269
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,280
What happened just now?

270
00:14:54,090 --> 00:14:55,090
I don't remember.

271
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,520
Anyway,

272
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:59,060
remember what I told you.

273
00:14:59,090 --> 00:15:00,550
If you ever find yourself in danger again,

274
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:01,990
protect yourself first.

275
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:04,250
But it's you I want to protect more.

276
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:05,940
Given that we came together,

277
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:07,600
we must make it back together.

278
00:15:11,410 --> 00:15:12,330
Shuo.

279
00:15:12,350 --> 00:15:13,150
What's wrong?

280
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:15,150
Nothing.

281
00:15:15,570 --> 00:15:17,110
Things are unpredictable tonight.

282
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:18,130
You don't have to force yourself.

283
00:15:18,130 --> 00:15:19,300
I promised I will help you,

284
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:20,680
and I will stand by that promise,

285
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:22,010
no matter what happens.

286
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:27,360
Nan Wan.

287
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,550
Be polite.

288
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:32,220
Thank you.

289
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,900
Are you really drinking that?

290
00:15:34,130 --> 00:15:35,690
Hua Lin doesn't seem to be taking us

291
00:15:35,690 --> 00:15:37,280
Eternals and demons seriously, does he?

292
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,870
He invited us to the banquet,

293
00:15:38,870 --> 00:15:40,130
but he is late himself.

294
00:15:40,810 --> 00:15:42,610
It's whatever the host prefers.

295
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:45,070
As an Eternal, you should be more patient.

296
00:15:45,090 --> 00:15:46,870
If it weren't for the Wutong Spirit Pill,

297
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,270
who would ever visit

298
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:49,560
such a deserted place?

299
00:15:49,770 --> 00:15:50,530
Would you?

300
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:52,080
His Majesty is here.

301
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:37,410
Something came up today,

302
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:38,850
which caused me to be late.

303
00:16:38,850 --> 00:16:40,240
I have been remiss in my duties to you all.

304
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,080
Allow me to

305
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,480
offer my apologies to everyone.

306
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,400
There's no need to be so polite.

307
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,890
Hurry up and burn the Wutong branch,

308
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:47,830
so that we can summon the third Heart Flame

309
00:16:47,830 --> 00:16:49,750
and select the winner of the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

310
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,290
I can't bear to

311
00:16:51,350 --> 00:16:52,350
stay in this

312
00:16:52,370 --> 00:16:54,050
Outlanders' City any longer.

313
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,460
Don't worry, Divinity.

314
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:56,740
The Wutong branch

315
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:58,160
is in the wooden box.

316
00:16:58,870 --> 00:17:01,100
All of you joined the Wutong Martial Arts Contest

317
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:02,790
to win the Wutong Spirit Pill.

318
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:05,609
The winner tonight

319
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:08,040
will win the pill.

320
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,220
But I

321
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:11,579
have something to tell you.

322
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,880
I've decided that

323
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,780
from today onwards,

324
00:17:14,990 --> 00:17:16,650
I'll open up Outlanders' City

325
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,980
and let the Outlanders enter the world.

326
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,000
From now on,

327
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,300
the Outlander Race

328
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:22,599
will no longer

329
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:24,400
be trapped in Outlanders' City.

330
00:17:24,619 --> 00:17:26,619
I ask that

331
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:28,290
you relay my words

332
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:29,970
to your sect after you return.

333
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:31,000
In the future,

334
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,690
as our Outlanders roam the world,

335
00:17:32,690 --> 00:17:33,890
I also ask for your

336
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:35,160
kind attention and care,

337
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:37,220
and not make things difficult for us.

338
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,560
What are you even thinking?

339
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:41,820
Empty talk from a fool.

340
00:17:43,690 --> 00:17:45,470
I know, right? What a joke.

341
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:47,030
What? How is that possible?

342
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:50,810
How can we stand with the Outlanders?

343
00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:59,070
Outside of Outlanders' City,

344
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:00,980
the Eternals, demons and humans

345
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,150
each have their own regions.

346
00:18:02,150 --> 00:18:04,260
How can there be any spare land for the Outlanders?

347
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:06,050
If the Outlander Race wants to step out of Outlanders' City,

348
00:18:06,050 --> 00:18:08,260
you must have a blessed place to reside in.

349
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:09,380
Would this place

350
00:18:09,410 --> 00:18:11,130
be carved out by us Eternals,

351
00:18:11,150 --> 00:18:12,670
or by the demons?

352
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:16,520
We demons have no room

353
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:18,340
to accommodate the Outlanders.

354
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:22,560
You Outlanders are born with weaker spiritual powers.

355
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:24,890
If you guys are living well in Outlanders' City,

356
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:26,960
what's the point of wandering around?

357
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,440
Right?

358
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:28,340
Yeah.

359
00:18:30,450 --> 00:18:32,090
-Yeah.
-Know your place.

360
00:18:32,940 --> 00:18:33,820
That's right.

361
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:36,040
Are the Eternals and demons

362
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,850
really unable to accommodate the Outlanders?

363
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:38,950
Oppressing the weak with power.

364
00:18:38,950 --> 00:18:40,410
It's the same everywhere.

365
00:18:40,860 --> 00:18:41,900
Just now,

366
00:18:41,930 --> 00:18:43,290
what I said

367
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,080
was just some of my thoughts.

368
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:47,050
Since you all think it's inappropriate

369
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:48,980
for Outlanders to enter the world,

370
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,180
I will

371
00:18:50,210 --> 00:18:51,690
give it some more thought.

372
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,150
Tonight,

373
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:55,530
let's wrap up the contest first.

374
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,060
As per the contest's traditions,

375
00:18:57,060 --> 00:18:57,780
we need

376
00:18:57,810 --> 00:18:59,420
the Three Races to gather

377
00:18:59,470 --> 00:19:01,010
and burn the Wutong branch together,

378
00:19:01,010 --> 00:19:03,810
in order to stimulate the third Heart Flame.

379
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:05,040
Well...

380
00:19:16,430 --> 00:19:18,130
So this is the Wutong branch?

381
00:19:25,610 --> 00:19:26,590
Now,

382
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,180
everybody, please

383
00:19:28,670 --> 00:19:30,530
burn the Wutong branch together.

384
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,710
It's lit.

385
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:15,370
Look!

386
00:20:15,390 --> 00:20:16,430
Look up!

387
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:21,120
-Heart Flame?
-That's the Heart Flame!

388
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:23,720
That's the third Heart Flame.

389
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:29,760
It has finally appeared.

390
00:20:30,010 --> 00:20:31,440
What's going on?

391
00:20:37,950 --> 00:20:39,250
Your Majesty,

392
00:20:39,690 --> 00:20:41,330
why is the third Heart Flame

393
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:43,230
looking so dull?

394
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,200
This Wutong Martial Arts Contest hosted by the Outlanders

395
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,800
is not a scam, is it?

396
00:20:47,390 --> 00:20:48,430
Indeed.

397
00:20:48,470 --> 00:20:50,550
The ritual is not over yet.

398
00:20:50,660 --> 00:20:51,580
Everyone,

399
00:20:51,690 --> 00:20:53,170
please calm down.

400
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:56,020
May I ask Ms. Bai

401
00:20:56,050 --> 00:20:58,430
to hand over the two Heart Flames that are with you?

402
00:20:58,430 --> 00:20:59,460
-What?
-She has both Heart Flames?

403
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:01,240
She has both Heart Flames?

404
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:06,140
-How did Bai Shuo get both Heart Flames?
-Didn’t Mu Jiu have the Heart Flame previously?

405
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:06,880
Heart Flame?

406
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:07,680
Her?

407
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:10,010
Hand over the Heart Flames. Give it up now!

408
00:21:11,230 --> 00:21:12,670
It seems that

409
00:21:12,690 --> 00:21:14,880
I can't hide anything from you, Your Majesty.

410
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,940
Mu Jiu gave me this Heart Flame.

411
00:21:16,970 --> 00:21:18,350
Are there rules that state

412
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:19,860
we are not allowed to give Heart Flames to each other?

413
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:21,140
Not really.

414
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,690
Then what do you mean, Your Majesty?

415
00:21:22,690 --> 00:21:24,000
Are you trying to take back

416
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,770
the Heart Flames that already have an owner?

417
00:21:25,770 --> 00:21:26,940
Of course not.

418
00:21:27,490 --> 00:21:28,990
The Wutong Heart Flame

419
00:21:29,020 --> 00:21:31,120
was created as one.

420
00:21:31,390 --> 00:21:33,090
The third Heart Flame

421
00:21:33,430 --> 00:21:35,030
needs the other two

422
00:21:35,050 --> 00:21:36,510
in order to be awakened.

423
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:39,080
-Hand it over!
-Hand it over!

424
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:40,480
-Hand it over!
-Hand it over!

425
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,440
Hand over the other two Heart Flames!

426
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,840
No one can own both of them.

427
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:44,840
Just her?

428
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:45,900
Give them up now!

429
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,830
Hand it over!

430
00:21:57,290 --> 00:21:58,390
During the Fenlan Banquet,

431
00:21:58,390 --> 00:22:00,100
whether those Eternals or demons attend,

432
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,040
the Bright Moon Palace

433
00:22:01,040 --> 00:22:03,280
would definitely be the focus of the King.

434
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:04,500
I heard that the Fox Clan

435
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:06,350
are best at hiding and running away.

436
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,140
You shall first sneak into the Underground Palace tonight

437
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,400
and see if Hua Yong is there.

438
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,600
If he's not in the Underground Palace,

439
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:12,600
try your best to bring him there.

440
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:13,890
I got it.

441
00:22:14,940 --> 00:22:15,820
What about you?

442
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:16,980
The third Heart Flame will be created after

443
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:18,280
the Eternals, demons and the King of Outlanders

444
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,690
burn the Wutong branch together.

445
00:22:19,690 --> 00:22:21,240
After we get the third Heart Flame,

446
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:22,650
I'll meet you in the Underground Palace.

447
00:22:22,650 --> 00:22:23,650
No problem.

448
00:22:23,670 --> 00:22:24,810
Leave it to me.

449
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:25,720
But,

450
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:27,570
you have to prepare two things for me.

451
00:22:27,570 --> 00:22:29,270
One of it is the map of the palace,

452
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:31,330
and the other is Hua Yong's portrait.

453
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:47,400
This is...

454
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:00,700
Look!

455
00:23:02,130 --> 00:23:03,060
The Heart Flame!

456
00:23:04,210 --> 00:23:05,140
The Heart Flame.

457
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:09,310
It's fused together.

458
00:23:29,610 --> 00:23:31,880
Now that the three heart flames have come together,

459
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,400
Your Majesty, please tell us

460
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:35,730
how we'll be deciding the final winner.

461
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,650
It's the Wutong Martial Arts Contest.

462
00:23:38,650 --> 00:23:40,490
Of course we'll need to fight.

463
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,600
What are you doing? Do you want to fight?

464
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:56,660
What are you doing?

465
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:00,500
-What are you doing?
-What are you doing?

466
00:24:00,970 --> 00:24:01,970
Hua Lin.

467
00:24:02,390 --> 00:24:04,060
What exactly do you want?

468
00:24:04,690 --> 00:24:06,610
You Eternals and demons

469
00:24:06,630 --> 00:24:08,470
are full of hypocrisy,

470
00:24:08,500 --> 00:24:10,150
deceiving the world for your own glory.

471
00:24:10,150 --> 00:24:12,590
Since you despise the Outlander Race this much,

472
00:24:12,590 --> 00:24:13,950
I will

473
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,320
kill all of you and bury your bones

474
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:16,980
here in the Outlanders' City.

475
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:33,850
What on earth is this place?

476
00:24:34,050 --> 00:24:35,370
It's so creepy.

477
00:24:43,260 --> 00:24:44,380
Hua Yong?

478
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:48,070
Hua Yong?

479
00:24:49,150 --> 00:24:52,320
Did the King of Outlanders use evil magic to offer this sacrifice?

480
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:54,030
Who is he offering this sacrifice to?

481
00:24:54,030 --> 00:24:54,610
No.

482
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:55,770
This is too strange.

483
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:58,300
I must not let Tian Huo and Bai Shuo in.

484
00:24:58,300 --> 00:24:59,830
I have to take Hua Yong away.

485
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:16,080
Where do you want to take him?

486
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:17,590
What are you doing?

487
00:25:17,620 --> 00:25:18,580
Let me tell you.

488
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,030
I'm the young master of the Fox Clan.

489
00:25:20,030 --> 00:25:21,850
If anything happens to me here in Outlanders' City,

490
00:25:21,850 --> 00:25:23,960
my aunt will definitely come for all of you.

491
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,910
As long as today's plans are successful,

492
00:25:25,910 --> 00:25:27,790
let alone Chang Mei,

493
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:29,620
your entire clan could come

494
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:32,100
and we Outlanders wouldn't even give a damn.

495
00:25:34,430 --> 00:25:35,910
Just now,

496
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:38,530
I've given you one last chance.

497
00:25:38,630 --> 00:25:41,360
If you are willing to give us Outlanders a way out,

498
00:25:41,390 --> 00:25:42,630
I can also

499
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:44,720
give you all a way out.

500
00:25:44,930 --> 00:25:46,030
But unfortunately,

501
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:47,920
you didn't cherish the opportunity.

502
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,480
Today's dire situation

503
00:25:49,740 --> 00:25:51,540
is entirely of your own making.

504
00:25:51,570 --> 00:25:52,470
Hua Lin.

505
00:25:52,570 --> 00:25:53,800
If you dare to act rashly,

506
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:55,500
Bright Moon Palace will definitely not spare your life.

507
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:57,810
You are restricted by the Magic Restriction,

508
00:25:57,810 --> 00:25:59,630
and you are also seriously injured.

509
00:25:59,630 --> 00:26:01,830
You don't have to pretend you're fine.

510
00:26:01,930 --> 00:26:03,410
At this point,

511
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:04,970
tonight,

512
00:26:04,990 --> 00:26:06,630
I ask that

513
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:08,140
you die here too.

514
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,040
Hua Lin.

515
00:26:09,070 --> 00:26:10,730
Even if you kill all the Eternals and demons in the city today,

516
00:26:10,730 --> 00:26:12,490
it only brings you temporary relief.

517
00:26:12,490 --> 00:26:14,560
The Eternals and demons will seek their revenge one day.

518
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,900
How can the Outlanders

519
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,920
stand against the fury of the world?

520
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,310
After tonight,

521
00:26:19,330 --> 00:26:20,560
we, the Outlander Race,

522
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:23,190
will no longer be trapped in this lonely city

523
00:26:23,260 --> 00:26:25,730
and be bullied by the Eternals and demons ever again.

524
00:26:25,730 --> 00:26:26,830
As Outlanders,

525
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:28,440
there'll be no place that is off-limits,

526
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:30,410
and there'll be nothing we cannot do.

527
00:26:30,410 --> 00:26:31,830
All rules

528
00:26:31,950 --> 00:26:33,950
shall be decided by the Outlanders.

529
00:26:35,390 --> 00:26:36,810
Decided by the Outlanders?

530
00:26:36,810 --> 00:26:38,210
-On what grounds?
-Yeah.

531
00:26:39,610 --> 00:26:40,740
Who’s afraid of who?

532
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,750
You are not just looking to vent your anger.

533
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,380
What exactly do you intend to do with the lives

534
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:46,100
of all these Eternals and demons?

535
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,660
Don't worry.

536
00:26:47,690 --> 00:26:48,770
Soon,

537
00:26:48,790 --> 00:26:50,310
you will know the answer.

538
00:26:51,470 --> 00:26:52,380
Your Majesty,

539
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:54,080
I advise you to stop now.

540
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:56,570
The Lanling disciples are at the inn.

541
00:26:56,710 --> 00:26:58,140
Once they figure out something is wrong,

542
00:26:58,140 --> 00:26:59,680
they will report to the sect immediately.

543
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,760
Within tonight,

544
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:01,810
the Five Eternals of Lanling

545
00:27:01,810 --> 00:27:03,160
will arrive in Outlanders' City.

546
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,640
I

547
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:06,230
forgot to tell you.

548
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,900
The Outlanders' City's barrier has been activated.

549
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:10,720
No one from outside can get in,

550
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:12,610
and no one from inside

551
00:27:12,810 --> 00:27:14,330
can similarly get out.

552
00:27:21,250 --> 00:27:22,980
How are we going to get out then?

553
00:27:23,930 --> 00:27:24,830
Tonight,

554
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:27,260
you'll only die here in Outlanders' City.

555
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:28,510
Take them down!

556
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,230
Get the Heart Flame!

557
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:51,480
Heart Flame!

558
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:54,160
Let's get out of here!

559
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:30,120
Zhao.

560
00:28:30,140 --> 00:28:31,020
Are you okay?

561
00:28:31,050 --> 00:28:32,050
I'm fine.

562
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:32,820
Let's get out first.

563
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:34,070
Do what you have to do.

564
00:28:34,730 --> 00:28:35,370
Let's go.

565
00:28:39,850 --> 00:28:40,530
Let's go.

