but from Outlanders.

850
00:39:43,810 --> 00:39:45,430
I was homeless when I was young.

851
00:39:45,430 --> 00:39:47,290
I've had enough of people's evil.

852
00:39:47,810 --> 00:39:49,870
I had to rely on the Mei family to make a comeback.

853
00:39:49,870 --> 00:39:51,160
That's why I became a tool for the Mei family

854
00:39:51,160 --> 00:39:52,760
to protect the royal family.

855
00:39:53,420 --> 00:39:55,940
Grandfather treated you like his own child.

856
00:39:56,720 --> 00:39:58,980
Mother treated you like her own brother.

857
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,760
How could you be so cold?

858
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:01,660
Cold?

859
00:40:01,780 --> 00:40:03,790
When your mother was forced to die,

860
00:40:03,870 --> 00:40:05,230
who wasn't cold?

861
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,510
Speaking of Mei Han,

862
00:40:08,690 --> 00:40:10,410
she did treat me well.

863
00:40:11,770 --> 00:40:13,090
But unfortunately,

864
00:40:13,290 --> 00:40:15,500
she was a blocker in my path to becoming king,

865
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:17,000
so she had to die.

866
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:20,160
What did you do to her?

867
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:23,620
Blame her for being too smart.

868
00:40:24,250 --> 00:40:26,360
Seven years ago, there was a famine in Outlanders' City.

869
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:28,720
I instigated the people to overthrow Hua Lin,

870
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,300
but she found out.

871
00:40:30,610 --> 00:40:31,490
Do you think

872
00:40:32,140 --> 00:40:33,580
I could still keep her?

873
00:40:35,650 --> 00:40:37,120
In order to kill her, I just had to

874
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:39,050
use a stone with the engraved words,

875
00:40:39,050 --> 00:40:40,400
"After the queen falls, the famine will be gone."

876
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:42,760
But I underestimated your love for her.

877
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:46,080
In the face of the people's demands,

878
00:40:46,110 --> 00:40:48,470
you chose to send her away and hide her.

879
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:50,980
So I had to change my plans.

880
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,650
It's you.

881
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,760
You used Hua Yong?

882
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:57,470
Yes.

883
00:40:57,490 --> 00:40:59,480
The one who exposed your mother's hiding place

884
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,520
was not Hua Yong.

885
00:41:02,210 --> 00:41:03,250
It was me.

886
00:41:03,830 --> 00:41:04,970
It was also me

887
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,800
who pinned the blame on Hua Yong.

888
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,620
I just didn't expect that

889
00:41:08,620 --> 00:41:10,710
when Mei Han stood up to face everything,

890
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:12,770
you were still trying to protect her.

891
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:16,750
I could only lie that I found the Fire Protection Pearl

892
00:41:16,750 --> 00:41:19,000
and suggested for Mei Han to fake her death.

893
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,680
You believed me,

894
00:41:20,710 --> 00:41:22,170
and Mei Han threw herself into the furnace,

895
00:41:22,170 --> 00:41:23,410
taking all the secrets with her

896
00:41:23,410 --> 00:41:24,890
and dying completely.

897
00:41:25,330 --> 00:41:27,150
Then, I just claimed that I was deceived by a sorcerer

898
00:41:27,150 --> 00:41:30,010
and didn't know that the Fire Protection Pearl was fake.

899
00:41:30,010 --> 00:41:31,330
You believed it too.

900
00:41:31,350 --> 00:41:33,070
I didn't blame you then

901
00:41:33,100 --> 00:41:35,240
because you're Mei Han's sworn brother.

902
00:41:35,240 --> 00:41:37,480
I didn't know you were such a beast.

903
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:38,830
I'll kill you!

904
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:48,960
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

905
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:57,980
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

906
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:07,840
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

907
00:42:05,090 --> 00:42:06,050
You mustn't die!

908
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:07,580
I haven't forgiven you yet.

909
00:42:07,580 --> 00:42:08,700
I won't let you die.

910
00:42:08,720 --> 00:42:10,120
You can't die.

911
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:13,950
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

912
00:42:10,710 --> 00:42:12,870
Hua Lin was indeed a good father.

913
00:42:13,110 --> 00:42:15,900
Seven years ago, you tried to wield the the Sword and destroy the city,

914
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:17,400
but got wounded by the sword's energy.

915
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:20,060
Did you think it was mere luck that you survived?

916
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:22,480
It was Hua Lin who sent you out of the city for medical treatment,

917
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,710
in order to save your life.

918
00:42:23,710 --> 00:42:26,460
It was only then you had the fortune of meeting Fan Yue.

919
00:42:26,460 --> 00:42:28,880
Why didn't you tell me?

920
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:32,620
I wanted you to leave the Outlanders' City,

921
00:42:33,090 --> 00:42:36,650
♫Across thousands of miles♫

922
00:42:34,350 --> 00:42:38,200
and live a carefree life.

923
00:42:38,230 --> 00:42:40,100
I don't want to repeat

924
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:42,860
your mother's tragedy.

925
00:42:41,330 --> 00:42:46,200
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

926
00:42:43,620 --> 00:42:45,260
No, no, don't die!

927
00:42:45,620 --> 00:42:46,660
Don't die!

928
00:42:46,750 --> 00:42:47,950
Father!

929
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:55,870
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

930
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:51,120
Don't die, Father!

931
00:42:51,140 --> 00:42:52,860
Don't die! Don't die!

932
00:42:57,020 --> 00:43:02,090
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

933
00:43:00,880 --> 00:43:03,430
Hearing you call me father,

934
00:43:05,460 --> 00:43:08,290
I can die without regrets.

935
00:43:17,810 --> 00:43:19,710
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

936
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:22,010
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

937
00:43:22,070 --> 00:43:23,860
♫My love brought tears♫

938
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:25,560
Father!

939
00:43:24,110 --> 00:43:25,880
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

940
00:43:26,140 --> 00:43:28,080
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

941
00:43:27,040 --> 00:43:28,800
No!

942
00:43:28,290 --> 00:43:29,510
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

943
00:43:29,750 --> 00:43:31,540
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

944
00:43:31,680 --> 00:43:33,240
No!

945
00:43:31,910 --> 00:43:33,890
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

946
00:43:34,250 --> 00:43:35,830
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

947
00:43:36,080 --> 00:43:37,730
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

948
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:40,110
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

949
00:43:40,420 --> 00:43:42,000
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

950
00:43:42,320 --> 00:43:44,110
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

951
00:43:44,380 --> 00:43:46,390
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

952
00:43:46,680 --> 00:43:48,180
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

953
00:43:48,380 --> 00:43:50,840
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

954
00:44:03,960 --> 00:44:05,310
Mei Han said I was wrong.

955
00:44:06,660 --> 00:44:08,260
Hua Lin said I was wrong.

956
00:44:08,280 --> 00:44:10,170
Even you said I was wrong.

957
00:44:10,920 --> 00:44:13,480
Today, I will show you exactly

958
00:44:13,510 --> 00:44:16,060
who can save the Outlanders' City.

959
00:44:22,660 --> 00:44:24,000
Still undecided?

960
00:44:24,130 --> 00:44:25,850
I'm not that patient.

961
00:44:25,870 --> 00:44:26,920
I'll count to three.

962
00:44:26,920 --> 00:44:28,040
If you don't choose,

963
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:29,300
you'll have no choice.

964
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:32,160
One.

965
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:36,760
Two.

966
00:44:41,120 --> 00:44:41,960
Three.

